      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's great. i think i'll use that. one more thing though, since we're worried about them feeling discouraged, do you think i should add a personal note or something at the end? or is there a specific way to phrase the part about the cloud stack so it doesn't sound like we're criticizing their current skills? just want to make sure it doesn't come off as a \"you failed\" vibe.",
      "source": "evaluator"
